							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Research Impact -->
		<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-amber-50">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
						Research Changing the Field
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						How our foundational research is influencing academic discourse and practical applications worldwide
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div>
						<h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Prompt Pattern Catalog Impact</h3>
						<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
							Our seminal research on prompt patterns has achieved over 1,500 citations and fundamentally changed how researchers and practitioners approach AI interaction design. The patterns we documented are now used in major university curricula and corporate training programs worldwide.
						</p>

						<div class="space-y-6">
							<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
								<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Academic Influence</h4>
								<p class="text-gray-600">Universities worldwide have incorporated our patterns into their AI and computer science curricula, training the next generation of AI practitioners.</p>
							</div>

							<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
								<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Industry Adoption</h4>
								<p class="text-gray-600">Major technology companies have integrated these patterns into their AI development workflows and employee training programs.</p>
							</div>

							<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md">
								<h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Global Standards</h4>
								<p class="text-gray-600">The framework has become a de facto standard for prompt engineering, referenced in countless research papers and practical implementations.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="relative">
						<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 via-orange-500 to-red-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white text-center">
							<h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">Citation Impact</h4>
							
							<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
								<div>
									<div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">1,500+</div>
									<div class="text-amber-100">Academic Citations</div>
								</div>
								<div>
									<div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">300+</div>
									<div class="text-amber-100">Book Chapter Citations</div>
								</div>
								<div>
									<div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">700K+</div>
