									Our research is actively shaping how the world approaches human-AI collaboration
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<!-- Decorative elements -->
						<div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-amber-200 rounded-full opacity-20"></div>
						<div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-32 h-32 bg-orange-200 rounded-full opacity-20"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Testimonials -->
		<section class="py-20 bg-white">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
						What Leaders Are Saying
					</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						Recognition from industry leaders, media, and the global AI community
